<h2>Changing utilities</h2>

<p>Overriding excising utilities is possible by using the same key. For example if you want more responsive overflow utility classes you can do this:</p>

{% highlight 'scss' %}
$custom: (
  "overflow": (
    responsive: true,
    property: overflow,
    values: visible hidden scroll auto,
  ),
);
{% endhighlight %}

<h2>Removing utilities</h2>

<p>Utilities can also be removed by changing the group key to <code>null</code>:</p>

{% highlight 'scss' %}
$custom: (
  "font-weight": null,
);
{% endhighlight %}
